                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-394-18510106 t18510106-394-punishment-68"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Russell Gurney, Esq., and the third Jury.</hi>
